  "detailed_description": "This is a game of fighting monsters and upgrading explosive equipment.<br>-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>After entering 'Slime's Choice', you will play the role of a slime and constantly become stronger in the game. Fight monsters, upgrade, and explode equipment.<br>Utilize various skills and techniques to obtain different equipment rewards from monsters to make characters stronger and stronger.<br>-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>Slime's Choice is a 3D single player adventure game that combines elements of RPG and other game genres.<br>It is a game with 2K maps and an open world.<br>Unique monsters, unique world style, make you a hero! Become a hero! Become the ruler of this world!<br>-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>There is also a lottery system in the game, and the lottery tickets generated can be used for lottery, allowing players to receive different random rewards for their efforts!<br>It also has a unique equipment recycling system, where you can recycle the collected equipment to obtain other resources, thus improving yourself and becoming stronger faster!<br>Collecting coins, you can purchase your favorite items in a random coin store, which is one of the ways to become stronger, but the better the item, the more coins it requires.<br>Let's start chopping monsters!!!<br>-----------------------------------------------------------------<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Monster</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918840/extras/3caceca70dd6bdeb3c90d4b3eb816ca4.poster.avif?t=1729636152\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918840/extras/3caceca70dd6bdeb3c90d4b3eb816ca4.webm?t=1729636152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shar